ith Adam as an Inner Circle email on Wednesday (if you haven=E2=80=99t upgr=
aded your subscription yet, you can and should do so here ( https://puck.ne=
ws/join/?_gl=3D1*1uuzgs4*_up*MQ..*_ga*OTQ4MTgzMzQuMTczODM2Mzk0MQ..*_ga_SEFD=
