greatest violinists of his time. It=E2=80=99s believed that Joachim premier=
ed Johannes Brahms=E2=80=99s Violin Concerto in D major, Op. 77, on this ve=
ry instrument in 1879. The catalog note features an 1868 photo of him holdi=
ng it.

