e sound quality=E2=80=94=E2=80=9Crich, complex, and full of depth,=E2=80=9D=
 according to Sotheby=E2=80=99s. The market for antique, high-end violins i=
s defined by scarcity: Stradivari made about 650 violins in his lifetime, o=
